sources.title: Ronnie and Julie - Full Movie
sources.description:
This modern spin on Shakespeare's classic tale of star-crossed lovers puts hockey, ice skating and devious mayoral politics between two feuding families and their ill-fated children (Joshua Jackson, "Dawson's Creek" and Margot Finley, "Opposite Sex").
